videos.description: Early in the first half, UConn's Amida Brimah swats the ball away from Northeastern, sending it into the stands.
videos.headline: UConn's Brimah rises up for a big block

videos.description: 1H (4:46) CONN Rodney Purvis made Layup. Assisted by Terry Larrier.
videos.headline: Terry Larrier block leads to Rodney Purvis fast break lay up through traffic

videos.description: Alex Murphy throws down a one-handed dunk in transition to give Northeastern a seven-point lead with just under four minutes to go against Connecticut.
videos.headline: Northeastern's Murphy throws down a dunk on the fast break
